e">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-publishes-video-of-islamic-jihad-terrorist-confessing-to-october-7-rape/0000018e-86b4-d641-abee-cfb720f40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的世俗和宗教弥赛亚公众对 10 月 7 日的看法截然不同。内战即将来临吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-secular-and-messianic-publics-see-oct-7-very-differently-is-civil-war-looming/0000018e-86b1-d641-abee-cfb7e1be0000</link><description>以色列社会面临着两种明确且不可调和的愿景——世俗公众和弥赛亚右派公众。后者正在利用政府所谓的司法改革和加沙的战火来追求自己的救赎梦想</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 21:38:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-secular-and-messianic-publics-see-oct-7-very-differently-is-civil-war-looming/0000018e-86b1-d641-abee-cfb7e1be0000</guid></item><item><title>缓冲区和控制走廊：以色列军队在加沙的工事是什么样子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/buffer-zone-and-control-corridor-what-israeli-armys-entrenchment-in-gaza-looks-like/0000018e-8556-df92-a5ff-e77e0d6a0000</link><description>以色列军队正在悄悄地建立一个缓冲区，占领加沙地带 16% 的领土，并建立一个控制走廊，以监视向北移动的巴勒斯坦人。这就是卫星图像中的样子</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 20:50:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/buffer-zone-and-control-corridor-what-israeli-armys-entrenchment-in-gaza-looks-like/0000018e-8556-df92-a5ff-e77e0d6a0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争中的性暴力：我们正在进行错误的对话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-28/ty-article/.highlight/sexual-violence-in-the-gaza-war-we-are-having-the-wrong-conversation/0000018e-8628-d9dd-a39f-ceead0bb0000</link><description>我们所目睹的否认主义、恐吓和厌女症对这场冲突中性暴力的受害者来说是有害的：那些站出来的人和那些没有站出来的人</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 20:49:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-28/ty-article/.highlight/sexual-violence-in-the-gaza-war-we-are-having-the-wrong-conversation/0000018e-8628-d9dd-a39f-ceead0bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院裁定被控强奸的墨西哥前外交官可引渡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/israeli-court-rules-mexican-ex-diplomat-accused-of-rape-extraditable/0000018e-869e-db91-afff-afde72720000</link><description>耶路撒冷地方法院下令对前墨西哥驻联合国教科文组织大使安德烈斯·罗默（Andres Roemer）实施电子脚镯软禁，然后可能引渡到墨西哥接受审判</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 20:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/israeli-court-rules-mexican-ex-diplomat-accused-of-rape-extraditable/0000018e-869e-db91-afff-afde72720000</guid></item><item><title>“如果人质是宗教犹太复国主义者或正统派，他们现在都已经回家了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/if-the-hostages-were-religious-zionists-or-haredim-they-would-all-be-home-by-now/0000018e-861f-d9dd-a39f-ceff85a00000</link><description>电影制片人大卫·沃拉赫的新片是对他成长的极端正统社会的严厉控诉。历时 16 年拍摄的《丹尼尔·奥尔巴赫》的主人公将自己描述为“犹太人、以色列人和反犹太主义者”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 20:11:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/if-the-hostages-were-religious-zionists-or-haredim-they-would-all-be-home-by-now/0000018e-861f-d9dd-a39f-ceff85a00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内政部长要求终止对约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦工人的禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-interior-minister-asks-for-end-to-ban-on-west-bank-workers/0000018e-8674-d0d3-a98e-d6ff063d0000</link><description>摩西·阿贝尔写信给总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡提出这一要求，称当前局势“助长了无法无天和违法行为”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 20:11:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-interior-minister-asks-for-end-to-ban-on-west-bank-workers/0000018e-8674-d0d3-a98e-d6ff063d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列被哈马斯扣为人质的照片荣获著名奖项，但招致批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/photo-of-israeli-being-taken-hostage-by-hamas-wins-renowned-award-drawing-criticism/0000018e-861c-d9dd-a39f-cefe1eb40000</link><description>批评者表示，选择沙尼·卢克（Shani Louk）被驱车进入加沙的照片是不合适的，而她的父亲则表示这张照片是历史的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 19:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/photo-of-israeli-being-taken-hostage-by-hamas-wins-renowned-award-drawing-criticism/0000018e-861c-d9dd-a39f-cefe1eb40000</guid></item><item><title>巴西博尔索纳罗请求法院允许接受内塔尼亚胡访问以色列的邀请</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/brazils-bolsonaro-requests-court-permission-to-accept-netanyahus-invite-to-israel/0000018e-865d-d49b-a3bf-f65f38530000</link><description>名誉扫地的巴西前领导人雅伊尔·博尔索纳罗正在寻求巴西当局的许可，归还被扣押的护照，以便他能够访问以色列。巴西联邦警察在调查他是否试图在 2023 年发动起义以继续掌权时没收了他的护照</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 19:32:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/brazils-bolsonaro-requests-court-permission-to-accept-netanyahus-invite-to-israel/0000018e-865d-d49b-a3bf-f65f38530000</guid></item><item><title>以色列颁奖仪式将在斯德洛特而不是耶路撒冷举行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-prize-ceremony-to-be-held-in-sderot-instead-of-jerusalem/0000018e-8653-d641-abee-cff7d9bb0000</link><description>教育部表示，自 10 月 7 日以来的首次颁奖典礼将在南部城市举行，并公布了获奖者的完整名单，其中包括企业家和民主活动人士埃亚尔·沃尔德曼 (Eyal Waldman)</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 19:30:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-prize-ceremony-to-be-held-in-sderot-instead-of-jerusalem/0000018e-8653-d641-abee-cff7d9bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德 (Yair Lapid) 首次赢得耶什·阿蒂德 (Yesh Atid) 党初选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/israeli-opposition-leader-yair-lapid-wins-first-ever-yesh-atid-party-primary/0000018e-8632-d9dd-a39f-cef251390000</link><description>前总理、现任反对党领袖拉皮德赢得了 52.5% 的选票，以 29 票击败挑战者拉姆·本·巴拉克（拉皮德 308 票，本·巴拉克 279 票）。结果比预期的要窄，一些人指责选民自满地认为拉皮德会获胜</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 18:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/israeli-opposition-leader-yair-lapid-wins-first-ever-yesh-atid-party-primary/0000018e-8632-d9dd-a39f-cef251390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 174 天：巴勒斯坦总理穆斯塔法组建新政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-174-palestinian-pm-mustafa-forms-new-government/0000018e-8609-d49b-a3bf-f61fcbcf0000</link><description>以色列国家安全委员会发布旅行警告，请勿前往土耳其、摩洛哥、埃及和约旦 ■ 以色列国防军表示，巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战恐怖分子承认他于 10 月 7 日强奸了以色列妇女 ■ 国际法院命令以色列采取措施，确保食品畅通无阻地进入加沙 ■ 巴勒斯坦穆斯塔法总理组建新政府 ■ 美国和以色列正在努力确定以色列代表团访问的新日期 ■ 战争结束 174 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 17:27:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-174-palestinian-pm-mustafa-forms-new-government/0000018e-8609-d49b-a3bf-f61fcbcf0000</guid></item><item><title>下令非法搜查巴勒斯坦妇女生殖器的以色列官员获得晋升</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officer-who-ordered-illegal-search-of-palestinian-womans-genitals-gets-promotion/0000018e-85bf-d9b3-abcf-87ff99520000</link><description>尽管指挥官对审讯人员的陈述与进行搜查的士兵的说法相矛盾，但对该事件的调查已于三年前终止</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 16:59:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officer-who-ordered-illegal-search-of-palestinian-womans-genitals-gets-promotion/0000018e-85bf-d9b3-abcf-87ff99520000</guid></item><item><title>斯莫特里奇和雷格夫部长在埃拉特房地产会议上在台下发出嘘声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/ministers-smotrich-and-regev-booed-off-stage-at-eilat-real-estate-conference/0000018e-8586-df92-a5ff-e7aeb77f0000</link><description>在度假城市埃拉特举行的房地产会议上，财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇和交通部长米里·雷格夫在一片嘘声中离开了讲台。一位与会者想知道为什么选择两位部长作为发言人。 “与现实完全脱节，”他说</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 16:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/ministers-smotrich-and-regev-booed-off-stage-at-eilat-real-estate-conference/0000018e-8586-df92-a5ff-e7aeb77f0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院命令以色列增加对加沙的人道主义援助，呼吁立即释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-28/ty-article/world-court-orders-israel-to-take-measures-to-ensure-food-gets-into-gaza/0000018e-85d9-d49b-a3bf-f5df73b40000</link><description>在南非请求世界法院采取额外措施后，国际法院命令以色列必须开放更多陆路过境点，以向加沙运送粮食和其他援助物资，“鉴于加沙人面临的生活条件不断恶化”，“特别是疫情蔓延”。饥荒和饥饿”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 16:16:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-28/ty-article/world-court-orders-israel-to-take-measures-to-ensure-food-gets-into-gaza/0000018e-85d9-d49b-a3bf-f5df73b40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的全日制托拉学生比犹太历史上任何时候都多。这已经变得无法忍受</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-has-more-full-time-torah-students-than-ever-in-jewish-history-its-intolerable/0000018e-84bf-df27-adee-a6ff10df0000</link><description>正是因为《托拉》研究对我来说如此珍贵，所以我想保留它，但要做到这一点，我们必须打破当今的范式，即成千上万的人在犹太学院学习，享受大量的国家福利，但不加入劳动力或以色列国防军。我们需要一个新模型</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:40:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-has-more-full-time-torah-students-than-ever-in-jewish-history-its-intolerable/0000018e-84bf-df27-adee-a6ff10df0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的草莓丰收曾经是丰收的象征，现在却是战争的另一个受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/gazas-strawberry-harvest-once-a-symbol-of-abundance-is-another-victim-of-the-war/0000018e-857c-d0d3-a98e-d7ffc2940000</link><description>自 1967 年以来，加沙人就以收获“红色黄金”草莓而自豪，草莓在加沙地带被称为“红色黄金”。现在，加沙北部约 40% 的耕地变成废墟，农民对未来感到担忧</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/gazas-strawberry-harvest-once-a-symbol-of-abundance-is-another-victim-of-the-war/0000018e-857c-d0d3-a98e-d7ffc2940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列向穆斯林占多数的国家和欧洲电视网发出旅行警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-travel-warnings-to-muslim-countries-and-the-eurovision/0000018e-8572-d6fd-a78f-a77ffe700000</link><description>以色列国家安全委员会敦促以色列人避免前往土耳其、摩洛哥、埃及和约旦。它补充说，计划参加瑞典欧洲电视网或法国奥运会的以色列人应避免表现出“以色列”特征</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 14:57:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-travel-warnings-to-muslim-countries-and-the-eurovision/0000018e-8572-d6fd-a78f-a77ffe700000</guid></item></channel></rss>